refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public BcMath\NumberBcMath\Number::sqrt
 intnullscale&null;


 Return the square root of $this.

&reftitle.errors;
This method throws a ValueError in the following cases:
This object is a negative value scale is outside the valid range BcMath\Number::scale of the result object is outside the valid range

  &reftitle.examples;

   BcMath\Number::sqrt example


<?php
var_dump(
    new BcMath\Number('2')->sqrt(),
    new BcMath\Number('2')->sqrt(3),
    new BcMath\Number('4')->sqrt(),
    new BcMath\Number('4')->sqrt(3),
);
?>


